pineapple (1.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release.
  * Framework detection for 23+ frameworks.
  * Dockerfile generation with multi-stage builds.
  * Optional automatic Docker build (--build / -b flag).
  * Docker daemon verification (pineapple verify docker).
  * Rich CLI with generate and verify subcommands.

